{"tid":2447922,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"打疫苗後中獎最新派彩限制(3月15日22:00)","createTime":"2021-03-15T14:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T14:47:29.000Z","uid":288304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8ea32fb48fb81200daa6c7a5df188dbecd023873","tid":2447922,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"打疫苗後中獎最新派彩限制(3月15日22:00)<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"blue\">15至30分鐘內 或/及 在4至6星期後發生</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權表示，新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會明天開會討論有關個案，重申本港現時使用的兩款疫苗安全有效，品質符合要求。他說，有按國際要求透過呈報機制，向衞生署通報相關個案；又指如果有疫苗過敏反應，<strong><span class=\"red\">通常在接種後15至30分鐘內發生</span></strong>，至於接種後相隔多久會出現嚴重情況，要視乎個案。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580505-20210314.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580505-20210314.htm&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=4cc3eef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580505-20210314.htm&h=10b82324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580505-20210314.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n委員會暫時未能確定面癱與疫苗有因果關係，指根據海外資料，接種疫苗後<span class=\"red\"><strong>面癱的情況一般在4至6星期後出現</strong></span>，原因是疫苗產生抗體及自身免疫反應令神經線受損，需要比較長時間，接種疫苗後兩小時或一日出現面癱並不常見。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2383077&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d81bc7a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2383077</a>"},{"pid":"1d2c164ecfede13cdecefa6e56ce7cb979cb477a","tid":2447922,"uid":279938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"龍門一分為二，一個縮細到啲草仲高過個龍門，另一個拉到去球場外"},{"pid":"0f7a4c4eb79d84f9856d606c8ac90f0273300768","tid":2447922,"uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"買個二手SSD人地都私保7日啦<br />\n堂堂一個偽政府D野保30分鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明中囯人有幾廢"},{"pid":"9757f8fcf825481bf36a490e991ab54281899beb","tid":2447922,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2c164ecfede13cdecefa6e56ce7cb979cb477a","tid":2447922,"uid":279938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"龍門一分為二，一個縮細到啲草仲高過個龍門，另一個拉到去球場外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:14:35.000Z","msg":"可能仲要兩個同時入晒先計"},{"pid":"2cfc35d4ed97b4ab757bad7a50a944c33c25c1fc","tid":2447922,"uid":39628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"死就話你遲左<br />\n面癱就話你早左<br />\ndllm<br />\n<br />\n一年都唔知有幾多單面癱, 咁都推到"},{"pid":"e234f6dd82304179f659d76f934e32a812e6c1eb","tid":2447922,"uid":52876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"都戇鳩, 只係保普通疲苗過敏反應, 咁保黎托柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那d過期疫苗,&nbsp;打到成個人癱左果d唔係過敏反應,&nbsp;咁就唔計?"},{"pid":"2826fafeb59c2dea8fa254f7f0d8ceb2b335135b","tid":2447922,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:25:06.000Z","msg":"資料咪係腥港人度拎lor"},{"pid":"f215962ffa5e611bc1931a0f28d40c7996752f93","tid":2447922,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"}]}